Update By: Jason Lim(Broadcom Corporation)
Update Time: 24-November-2024 23:00:27

Latest Response: 
Hello, Kim WonKyun,
 
Please check "BT_A2DP_OFFLOAD_ENABLED" setting in your mk files first.
If you use "BT_A2DP_OFFLOAD_ENABLED := n" setting, "ro.vendor.nx.aud.a2dp_offload=1" setting will be skipped.
bcm.mk (device\broadcom\common)

ifeq ($(BT_A2DP_OFFLOAD_ENABLED),y)
PRODUCT_PROPERTY_OVERRIDES += \
   ro.vendor.nx.aud.a2dp_offload=1
endif
 
Thanks,
Jason Lim

=========================================================================================

